data.text: @enews I have seen him a volleyball tournaments with his daughters, so not sure how true it is that they don’t want to see him.

@enews Idk about CA. But in MA. There is a age limit for the children to make their own decision at 14 yrs they are able to decide who they want to live with and if they want to see the other parent or not you can not force a child to see someone even if it’s the other parent
